Script info:
  description: Get complete results by getting all paginated ones.
  hidden: true

Input parameters:
  url: Spotify url to GET

---
${all}: [ ]
${offset}: 0

Repeat:

  GET: ${input.url}&limit=50&offset=${offset}
  As: ${result}

  Add to:
    ${all}: ${result.items}
    ${offset}: 50

  until:
    empty: ${result.items}

Output: ${all}